gym_denki_040_receptionist_00:
[VAR BD06(0000)]Welcome to the Levincia Gym,
[VAR TRNAME(0000)].
gym_denki_040_receptionist_01:
Are you ready to challenge Gym Leader Iono,
the Supercharged Streamer?
gym_denki_040_receptionist_02:
Very well. Allow me to show you to the
battle court.
gym_denki_040_receptionist_03:
Understood. Please feel free to come speak to
me whenever you’re ready.
gym_denki_040_denki_entry_01: Ladies and gentlemens! Are you readyyyyyy?![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_01:
Your eyeballs are MINE—caught in my
Electroweb! Whosawhatsit? Iono!\c
’Ello, ’ello, hola! Ciao and bonjour![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_15: It’s time for the Iono Zone, everybody![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_02:
Today’s challenger is flyin’ high like a Wattrel!
Iiit’s [VAR TRNAME(0000)]! Yayyy![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_03:
[VAR BD06(0000)]How’re ya feelin’ about this battle,
[VAR TRNAME(0000)]?[VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_04a:
Boom! We got a straight talker here, ’eyyy?
No nonsense! I like it![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_04b:
Hey heyyy! We got a lively one here! You’d make
a gnarly influencer, friendo![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_04c:
Oh ho hooo? Playing timid, eh? Nyahaha! I don’t
hate it![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_05:
All righty, then! Who’s ready to see me kick
some butt?[VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_06:
Looks like you’re all gettin’ hyped! Ah... Thank ye
muchly, Electro King![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_07:
Let’s get this show on the road! How strong is
our challenger? I ’unno! Let’s find out together![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_08:
Our challenger came out victorious! Well done,
[VAR TRNAME(0000)]![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_09:
I hate to say it, but I lost! Thanks for cheerin’ me
on anywho, my loyal fans![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_10:
Well then! What does our challenger get for
beating me—the lean, mean streamin’ queen?\r
I’ll tell ya! [VAR TRNAME(0000)], you win...[VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_12:
Screencap this quick! This’ll be a shot you’ll
wanna save in your brainspaces forever![VAR 0114(0019)]

By the bysies, with all 8 Gym Badges, you can
catch Poké pals of any level, and they’ll ALL\r

gym_denki_040_denki_waza:
And as my thanks for such a sweet pic, I’mma
give you a Tee Em![VAR 0114(0019)]
gym_denki_040_denki_13:
If any of you found our electrifying battle to be—
bzzzt!—shocking, go smash that subscribe button![VAR 0114(0019)]

Your eyeballs are MINE—caught in my
Electroweb! Whosawhatsit? Iono the\r
